{
  "openapi": "3.1.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "MoreLogin Automation Agent API",
    "description": "Remote-control API for MoreLogin browser profiles and cloud phone automation.\n\n## Quick Start\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| **API Key ID** | `[PLACEHOLDER:AGENT_API_KEY_ID]` |\n| **API Key Secret** | `[PLACEHOLDER:AGENT_API_KEY_SECRET]` |\n| **Local URL** | `http://127.0.0.1:18080` |\n| **Public URL (ngrok)** | `https://[PLACEHOLDER:agent.example.com]` |\n\n## Authentication\n\nAll endpoints **except** `POST /agent/v1/callbacks/morelogin` (from loopback) require HMAC-SHA256 via 4 headers:\n\n| Header | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `X-API-Key` | `[PLACEHOLDER:AGENT_API_KEY_ID]` |\n| `X-Timestamp` | Unix timestamp in seconds |\n| `X-Nonce` | Unique UUID per request |\n| `X-Signature` | HMAC-SHA256 hex digest |\n\n**Canonical string:** `{METHOD}\\n{PATH}\\n{TIMESTAMP}\\n{NONCE}\\n{SHA256(BODY)}`\n\n- `PATH` is URL path **only** — does **not** include query string\n- `SHA256(BODY)` is lowercase hex; empty body uses SHA-256 of `\"\"`\n\n**Signature:** `HMAC_SHA256_HEX(\"[PLACEHOLDER:AGENT_API_KEY_SECRET]\", canonical_string)`\n\n### Limits\n\n| Limit | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Nonce TTL | 300 s |\n| Timestamp replay window | 120 s |\n| Max request body | 2 MB |\n| Rate limit | 60 req/min per key |\n\n## Command Modes\n\n| Mode | Commands |\n|------|----------|\n| **Sync** | `profile.list`, `profile.start`, `profile.stop`, `profile.status`, `cloudphone.list`, `cloudphone.power_on`, `cloudphone.power_off`, `cloudphone.exec_command`, `schedule.cancel` |\n| **Always Async** | `browser.open_and_run`, `file.attach_from_url`, `file.download`, `schedule.create` |\n\n## Job Status Values\n\n`queued` → `running` → `completed` | `failed`\n",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "contact": {
      "name": "MoreLogin Support",
      "email": "support@morelogin.com",
      "url": "https://morelogin.com"
    },
    "license": {
      "name": "Proprietary"
    }
  },
  "externalDocs": {
    "description": "Full API guides",
    "url": "https://[PLACEHOLDER:agent.example.com]/docs"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "http://127.0.0.1:18080",
      "description": "Local agent"
    },
    {
      "url": "https://[PLACEHOLDER:agent.example.com]",
      "description": "Public"
    },
    {
      "url": "https://{agent-host}",
      "description": "Custom tunnel",
      "variables": {
        "agent-host": {
          "default": "agent.example.com"
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "description": "Agent and upstream health checks"
    },
    {
      "name": "Diagnostics",
      "description": "MoreLogin diagnostics"
    },
    {
      "name": "Commands",
      "description": "Execute automation commands"
    },
    {
      "name": "Jobs",
      "description": "Async job tracking"
    },
    {
      "name": "Callbacks",
      "description": "Callback ingestion and dead-letter management"
    }
  ],
  "security": [
    {
      "HmacAuth": []
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/agent/v1/health": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "Health"
        ],
        "summary": "Agent Health Check",
        "description": "Returns agent health including DB connectivity and worker heartbeat.\n",
        "operationId": "health_check",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Health status",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "allOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ResponseEnvelope"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "data": {
                          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HealthData"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "example": {
                  "success": true,
                  "data": {
                    "status": "ok",
                    "agent_id": "agent-001",
                    "database": {
                      "ok": true
                    },
                    "worker": {
                      "alive": true,
                      "last_heartbeat": "2026-03-25T00:00:00Z",
                      "age_seconds": 3
                    },
                    "sqlite_pragma": {
                      "journal_mode": "wal",
                      "synchronous": "1"
                    }
                  },
                  "error": null,
                  "request_id": null,
                  "agent_id": "agent-001",
                  "job_id": null,
                  "upstream_code": 0,
                  "upstream_msg": "ok"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized"
          },
          "429": {
            "$ref": "#/components/responses/RateLimited"
          },
          "500": {
            "$ref": "#/components/responses/InternalError"
          }
        }
      }
    },
